    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ALMultiParamTask, ALPartitionEvaluationTask, ALPrequentialEvaluationTask
    public abstract class ALMainTask
extends MetaMainTask
    This class provides a superclass for Active Learning tasks, which enables convenient searching for those tasks for example when showing a list of available Active Learning tasks. Furthermore, it specifies the type of threads being used as ALTaskThread.
    Version:
